Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然見到了「艾利尊戰役」\N當時羅曼洛夫的部下羅博特上等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.42,0:00:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如您所見 基本不開口說話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.76,0:00:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 他無法出任證人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.05,0:00:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火之畫…火的戰場…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.69,0:00:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 多虧公安的通行證
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.31,0:00:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此簡單就能見面的理由就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.90,0:00:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他明天移送到你那之前 會把他在HESNER公司工作時的資料給你傳過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.83,0:00:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.80,0:00:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像白費工夫了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 但是從她沒受到妨礙 平安無事這一點上能得出點結論
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.50,0:00:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人有沒有留下任何證據的自信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.48,0:00:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又或者羅曼洛夫體制並非如此團結
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:08.79,LOGO1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,300)}{\fad(0,1700)}極影&薔薇園
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:08.79,LOGO,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,300)}{\fad(0,1700)}極影&薔薇園
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.05,0:01:10.53,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Squeez'n step on it hard
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.05,0:01:10.53,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}跨上機車 馬力全開
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:13.78,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Try to feet my heart beat
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:13.78,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}試著去感受心的律動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.82,0:01:17.34,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,High,as high as you can
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.82,0:01:17.34,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}飛躍吧！盡你所能！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.45,0:01:20.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All your blood will turn to fountain water
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.45,0:01:20.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}血液沸騰有如泉湧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.95,0:01:24.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're surrounded by plot in this universe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.95,0:01:24.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}大千世界，我們的週遭佈滿陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.43,0:01:28.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wash away the stain of blood with tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.43,0:01:28.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}用淚水洗去血染的污點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.14,0:01:31.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot look,or they will spell on you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.14,0:01:31.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}讓雙眼避開所有的蠱惑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.44,0:01:34.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wind of fuego will lead us through
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.44,0:01:34.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"烈焰"之風會引領我們向前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.74,0:01:51.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.74,0:01:51.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}探光明 求真實 我與它們融與一體
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.98,0:01:55.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found guide-in line in the raging world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.98,0:01:55.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在波濤洶湧的世界裡找尋指引
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:59.92,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you see,in the sky,even in this insane world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:59.92,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}舉目看 天湛藍 縱然世界狂亂不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:01.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ride on Back
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:01.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}仍有背騎的身影穿梭其間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.21,0:02:04.17,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All we need is your sympathy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.21,0:02:04.17,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我們需要的是你們的共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.19,0:02:07.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We make the history of our own
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.19,0:02:07.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}一同去創造屬於我們的歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.44,0:02:10.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.44,0:02:10.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}探光明 求真實 我與它們融與一體
